,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:52:22.000Z","msg":"垃圾家長，個仔／女病咗都推佢返學，驚死蝕底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3e94a082fa96bf8def0ccde45e854cbf2c1efe","tid":551840,"uid":166663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da1b25aeabe51520b6f85cb5dfac0e42bded4106","tid":551840,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8559aa1f88ba21319c8ccf6005e8693e7ebcdb6a","tid":551840,"uid":166663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"769a818300921e978fa4c76b1a2b234d9a6f63b4","tid":551840,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:38:34.000Z","msg":"已經死左成佰幾人啦今次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:45:13.000Z","msg":"仲未倒SARS級別。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:49:24.000Z","msg":"d virus 會異變...香港一定死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T06:59:05.000Z","msg":"特衰正苦淨係識隱瞞疫情﹐我地d小市民可以點。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上次有個女童有抗藥性肺努﹐唔去覆診唔肯食藥。<br />\n仲週街走。最後好彩捉左去強制隔離。<br />\n但仆街正苦唔肯講個死女包去過邊區﹐住係邊區。<br />\n真係好仆街。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60852f4210f1b5eeb27b2fc90431f0f4a92d65d1","tid":551840,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T07:43:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c384296473057e9add2ceab37d241a39c21524c","tid":551840,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T08:19:06.000Z","msg":"睇死雙非兒童，成日返大陸吸菌，而家返香港播菌，死返上去啦"}]}